  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CurrentUser
    Current User class extends Spring User class by adding a new field user of type User (entity which stores data of users).
    OddsCalculator
    OddsCalculator is a class containing various methods for generating odds of football matches.
    SpringDataUserDetailsService
    SpringDataUserDetailsService implements UserDetailsService interface overriding its loadUserByUsername method as to return custom CurrentUser class
